title: Ep. - 439 - WE NEED TO TALK ABOUT COSBY EXECUTIVE PRODUCER
description:
Kate discusses Real Housewives of Salt Lake City, American Rockstars, and Celebrity Big Brother.

 

Katie King, Executive Producer of We Need to Talk About Cosby, a Showtime 4-part series by Comic-director W. Kamau Bell exploring Bill Cosby's life and work, weighing his actions against his indisputable influence through interviews with comedians, cultural commentators, journalists and women who share their personal encounters with him.

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
